Class GuiController

java.lang.Object
com.comp2042.ui.GuiController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class GuiController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
JavaFX controller for the gameplay scene. It renders the board layers, handles input, and delegates gameplay actions to GameController.
